 Nijisanji EN的Luca Kaneshiro揭晓VRChat世界庆祝《Luxiem》两周年并与会员一起挑战游戏https://www.moguravr.com/luxiem-hole/井文 Wed, 20 Dec 2023 03:02:33 +0000 VTuberにじさんじVRChatにじさんじEN https://www.moguravr.com/?p=242381 <p> VTuber团体“NIJISANJI EN”所属单位“Luxiem”的Luca Kaneshiro在“VR […]中创造了团体2周年纪念世界“Luxiem Hole”</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/luxiem-hole/">后Nijisanji EN的Luka Kaneshiro揭开了VRChat世界的面纱，以纪念《Luxiem》两周年，与成员一起挑战游戏，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> VTuber团体“ <a href="https://twitter.com/nijisanji_world" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NIJISANJI EN</a> ”的小分队“Luxiem”所属的<a href="https://twitter.com/luca_kaneshiro" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Luca Kaneshiro</a>在“VRChat”中公开了团体2周年纪念世界“Luxiem Hole”。我们与“Luxiem”成员一起直播了世界各地的比赛。</p><p> *截至12月20日，“Luxiem Hole”是一个私人世界，一般用户无法在“VRChat”上玩。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Luxiem VR 墙上的洞游戏秀 - 两周年纪念特别活动！#Luxiem2ndAnniversary" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QSB5fkJziFw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok6ef38zhdls-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok6ef38zhdls-1024x532.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok6ef38zhdls-1024x532.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok6ef38zhdls-300x156.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok6ef38zhdls-768x399.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok6ef38zhdls-jpg.webp 1273w" width="1024" height="532" /></a></p><p> “Luxiem Hole”是一个游戏世界，您站在世界内舞台上设置的跑道上，摆出与从后面接近的“剪切板”相同的姿势。如果你的姿势失败并撞到墙上，你就会掉进你前面的水池里。</p><p> 《Luxiem》的 Ike Eveland、Vox Akuma 和 Shu Yamino 参与了发行。矢美野州 (Yami Noshu) 佩戴全身追踪设备接受了挑战。他展示了如何以绝妙的“中腰姿势”穿墙而过。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.pph46lclicpb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.pph46lclicpb-1024x534.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.pph46lclicpb-1024x534.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.pph46lclicpb-300x156.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.pph46lclicpb-768x400.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.pph46lclicpb-jpg.webp 1257w" width="1024" height="534" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.9n0uk02u40gy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.9n0uk02u40gy-1024x529.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.9n0uk02u40gy-1024x529.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.9n0uk02u40gy-300x155.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.9n0uk02u40gy-768x397.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.9n0uk02u40gy-jpg.webp 1274w" width="1024" height="529" /></a><br /> （暗野树先生试图突破墙壁）</p><p>玩了几次游戏后，Vox 尝试提高难度。第一个我顺利通过了，但第二个却撞到了我，掉进了水池里。与《暗之书》的设定（难度）相比，你可以看到，通过面板是极其困难的。</p><p> <a href="h